title: Johnny Winter - Live Bootleg Series Vol. 6 [FLAC]
description:
This CD consists of very rare and historical musical moments from the personal archives of Johnny Winter. The original source tapes were not made on the most advanced equipment of the time, but just to have a glimpse into the power of these rare live performances, makes the listen an enjoyable Johnny Winter experience. (publisher notes)


Johnny Winter - Live Bootleg Series Vol. 6
